0that%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Boff-premise%26quot%3B%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20or%20those%20at%20supermarkets%20and%20convenience%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20grew%20by%20more%20than%2050%25%20between%202023%20and%202024.%20Athletic%20is%20now%20the%20most%20popular%20brand%20in%20the%20category%2C%20holding%20more%20than%2019%25%20market%20share%2C%20Shufelt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20company%20has%20worked%20hard%20to%20match%20the%20price%20of%20widely%20distributed%20craft%20beer.%20Six-packs%20of%20Athletic%20are%20typically%20priced%20between%20%249.99%20and%20%2410.99%20on%20retail%20shelves.%20The%20price%20is%20budget-friendly%2C%20even%20after%C2%A0Athletic%20re-engineered%20nearly%20every%20step%20of%20the%20brewing%20process%20to%20make%20its%20products%20free%20of%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20some%20may%20assume%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20alcohol%20should%20make%20NA%20beer%20less%20expensive%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20can%20cost%20just%20as%20much%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20more%20%E2%80%94%20to%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20Shufelt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mocktails-expensive-ingredients-na-alcohol-spirits-wine-prices-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736499662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677ebab08951662c9f1f3fbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mocktails-expensive-ingredients-na-alcohol-spirits-wine-prices-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20many%20Americans%20turn%20to%20non-alcoholic%20alternatives%20like%20mocktails%2C%20sticker%20shock%20can%20be%20a%20common%20reaction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mocktails-expensive-ingredients-na-alcohol-spir