d%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.danabull.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Econsultant%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bswore%20off%20investing%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%20Managing%20properties%20is%20time-intensive%2C%20noted%20the%20mother%20of%20four.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20a%20charming%20single-family%20in%20Marblehead%20came%20on%20the%20market%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023%2C%20she%20broke%20her%20promise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20little%20place%20in%20my%20town%20caught%20my%20eye%2C%20and%20I%20really%20wanted%20somebody%20else%20to%20buy%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20when%20the%20interest%20rates%20were%20the%20highest%20that%20they've%20ever%20been%2C%20like%207.75%25%2C%20so%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20buy%20anything.%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'You%20know%20what%2C%20I'll%20do%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c865b5a2-abf4-4427-b773-46413f2afd35%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EListing%20it%20as%20a%20mid-term%20rental%20to%20combat%20high%20rates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHigher%20interest%20rates%20mean%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment.%20For%20an%20investor%2C%20that%20can%20make%20it%20more%20challenging%20to%20generate%20positive%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20make%20the%20numbers%20work%20on%20her%20latest%20acquisition%2C%20Bull%20decided%20to%20experiment%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bmid-term%20rental%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20targets%20people%20looking%20to%20stay%20for%20one%20month%20or%20more%2C%20but%20less%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20first%20experience%20with%20something%20other%20than%20a%20long-term%20rental.%20I'm%20kind%20of%20in%20uncharted%20waters%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull%2C%20who%20plans%20to%20test%20out%20the%20mid-term%20rental%20strategy%20for%20at%20least%2018%20months.%20It's%20more%20work%20than%20managing%20a%20long-term%20tenant%2C%20but%20she%20said%20she's%20bringing%20in%20more%20revenue%20doing%20shorter%20leases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20could%20earn%20even%20more%20if%20she%20had%20more%20time%20and%20could%20lease%20the%20unit%20herself%2C%20rather%20than%20working%20with%20an%20agent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20leasing%20agent%20who%20I%20pay%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20because%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20continue%20to%20keep%20it%20leased%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20strategy%20for%20anybody%20that%20has%20the%20availability%20to%20do%20the%20leasing%20on%20their%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leasing%20aspect%20of%20the%20mid-term%20rental%20strategy%20is%20the%20most%20challenging%20because%20it's%20less%20mainstream%20than%20the%20short-%20and%20long-term%20strategy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20a%20long-term%20rental%2C%20you%20know%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20on%20Zillow%20or%20work%20with%20a%20real-estate%20agent.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20short-term%20rental%2C%20you%20also%20have%20set%20channels%3A%20You%20have%20Airbnb%2C%20Vrbo%2C%26quot%3B%20Bull%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20website%20called%20Furnished%20Finder%20geared%20toward%20mid-term%20rentals%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20very%20well%20known%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20nearly%20as%20big%20as%20something%20like%20Airbnb.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20advertises%20her%20place%20on%20Furnished%20Finder%2C%20takes%20it%20on%20and%20off%20Zillow%20depending%20on%20when%20it's%20available%2C%20and%20sends%20neighborhood%20mailers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20helps%20that%20she's%20starting%20to%20understand%20her%20typical%20tenant%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20trend%20is%20that%20grandparents%20want%20to%20come%20and%20help%20out%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20but%20the%20parents%20don't%20have%20room%20in%20their%20home%2C%20or%20the%20grandparents%20want%20their%20own%20space%2C%20so%20that%20has%20been%20my%20target%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7549057-c760-476c-ad58-7cda678bffb2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMid-term%20rentals%20as%20a%20viable%20strategy%20for%202025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBull%20doesn't%20expect%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20drop%20in%202025.%20She%20also%20doesn't%20advise%20letting%20rates%20or%20other%20factors%20outside%20your%20control%20dictate%20when%20you%20buy%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20base%20my%20whole%20plan%20around%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20keep%20hearing%20rates%20are%20supposed%20to%20drop%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20current%20rates%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20historical%20average.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20kind%20of%20where%20rates%20sit.%20So%2C%20if%20they%20were%20to%20drop%2C%20that%20would%20be%20great%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20banking%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20financially%20prepared%20to%20invest%20in%20real%20estate%20in%202025%2C%20rather%20than%20waiting%2C%20run%20the%20numbers%20to%20see%20if%20a%20short-%20or%20mid-term%20rental%20could%20make%20sense%20in%20your%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20some%20alternative%20leasing%20approaches.%20Usually%2C%20they're%20more%20lucrative%20if%20they're%20shorter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull.%20%26quot%3BOne%20idea%20would%20be%20to%20start%20with%20something%20like%20an%20Airbnb%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20transitioning%20after%20two%20or%20three%20years%20into%20something%20more%20passive%2C%20like%20a%20long-term%20rental.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReal%20estate%20is%20a%20long-term%20game%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20look%20beyond%20year%20one%20%E2%80%94%20the%20numbers%20are%20always%20going%20to%20be%20tight%20year%20one%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20market%20conditions%20are%20%E2%80%94%20so%2C%20what%20are%20your%20projections%20going%20to%20be%20by%20year%20five%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%2C%20what%20can%20you%20do%20in%20the%20interim%20to%20maybe%20make%20this%20property%20work%3F%20That%20would%20be%20focusing%20on%20neighborhoods%20and%20communities%20where%20you%20can%20balance%20both%20of%20these%20plays%3A%20It's%20going%20to%20attract%20a%20short-term%20rental%20tenant%20but%2C%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20can%20pivot%20into%20a%20longer-term%20tenant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20likely%20what%20she's%20going%20to%20do%2C%20especially%20if%20she%20can%20refinance%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBull%20has%20already%20refinanced%20once%2C%20which%20shaved%20about%20%24250%20off%20her%20mortgage%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20it%20if%20they%20dropped%20again%20and%20I%20could%20save%20another%20250.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20probably%20would%20transition%20it%20to%20a%20long-term%20rental%20because%20it%20would%20be%20lucrative%20enough%20and%20less%20of%20a%20headache%2C%20but%20right%20now%20I'm%20just%20experimenting%20for%20my%20own%20curiosity%20and%20I%20want%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20this%20niche.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-strategy-during-high-rate-environments-mid-term-rentals-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736499602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67801ac58951662c9f1f7701%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-strategy-during-high-rate-environments-mid-term-rentals-2025-