%20opposite%20of%20what%20he%20initially%20preached.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20not%20significantly%20affected%20him%2C%20at%20least%20not%20electorally.%20His%20onward%20march%20has%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Delhi%20appears%20to%20be%20different%20from%20what%20it%20was%20in%202015%20and%202020.%20On%20February%205%20this%20year%2C%20when%20Delhi%20goes%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20Kejriwal%20could%20face%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20regain%20power.%20In%20short%2C%20this%20verdict%20will%20reflect%20whether%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20forget%20and%20forgive%20his%20deviations%20and%20failure%20to%20deliver%20on%20his%20promises.%20There's%20a%20reason%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20term%20(2015-2020)%2C%20Kejriwal%20introduced%20numerous%20initiatives%20and%20created%20a%20heavy%20buzz%3A%20free%20electricity%20up%20to%20200%20units%2C%20free%20water%2C%20Mohalla%20clinics%2C%20improvements%20in%20government-run%20hospitals%2C%20upgrades%20in%20the%20appearance%20of%20government%20school%20classrooms%2C%20and%20a%20seemingly%20genuine%20fight%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20the%20division%20of%20power.%20He%20also%20made%20bold%20claims%20about%20ways%20to%20reduce%20Delhi's%20pollution%2C%20among%20other%20promises.%20Cut%20to%20the%20current%20term%20(2020-2025)%2C%20Kejriwal%20has%20little%20substantive%20progress%20to%20showcase.%20This%20period%20has%20mostly%20been%20marked%20by%20negative%20news%20for%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20reasons%20why%20Kejriwal%20could%20face%20a%20real%20challenge%20this%20time%20around%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20the%20four%20main%20AAP%20leaders%E2%80%94Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Satyendra%20Jain%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%94are%20out%20on%20bail%20after%20spending%20considerable%20time%20in%20jail%20in%20relation%20to%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%20Kejriwal%20spent%20over%20five%20months%20in%20judicial%20custody%20at%20Tihar%20jail%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20remained%20behind%20bars%20for%2017%20months%2C%20Satyendra%20Jain%20was%20in%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20in%20custody%20for%20six%20months.%20It%20couldn't%20have%20got%20worse%20for%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20'anti-corruption'%20crusader.%20Both%20Kejriwal%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20and%20his%20Deputy%2C%20Sisodia%2C%20were%20named%20in%20the%20liquor%20scam.%20It%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20for%20the%20courts%20to%20reach%20a%20final%20verdict%2C%20with%20the%20process%20likely%20dragging%20out%20from%20the%20lower%20courts%20to%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20ultimately%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Kejriwal%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20position%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail%20due%20to%20conditions%20imposed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20prevented%20him%20from%20attending%20office%20and%20signing%20official%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20the%20renovation%20worth%20over%20%E2%82%B933%20crore%20that%20Kejriwal%20got%20done%20for%20his%20official%20residence%20on%206%20Flag%20Staff%20Road%E2%80%94at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20public%20exchequer%E2%80%94could%20potentially%20become%20a%20glaring%20symbol%20of%20the%20contradiction%20between%20what%20Kejriwal%20practised%20and%20preached%2C%20or%20even%20once%20stated%20in%20an%20affidavit.%20The%20pictures%20of%20the%20fixtures%20and%20fittings%20in%20the%20toilets%2C%20gym%2C%20sauna%2C%20jacuzzi%2C%20kitchen%2C%20living%20rooms%2C%20and%20corridors%20are%20beyond%20the%20comprehension%20of%20ordinary%20citizens.%20The%20CAG%20report%20has%20provided%20an%20itemised%20list%20of%20purchases%20for%20the%20renovation%2C%20including%20%E2%82%B996%20lakh%20for%20curtains%2C%20%E2%82%B939%20lakh%20for%20kitchen%20equipment%2C%20%E2%82%B94.80%20lakh%20for%20a%20minibar%2C%20%E2%82%B916.27%20lakh%20for%20silk%20carpets.%20The%20list%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20Kejriwal's%20much-hyped%20claim%2C%20that%20he%20enhanced%20the%20public%20health%20sector%20and%20transformed%20Delhi's%20education%20system%20with%20world-class%20institutions%2C%20has%20come%20under%20significant%20scrutiny.%20The%20gap%20between%20the%20hype%20and%20reality%20is%20now%20too%20evident%20to%20overlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20last%20year%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20irregularities%20were%20uncovered%20by%20the%20vigilance%20and%20health%20departments%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20Mohalla%20clinics%20and%20some%20hospitals%20run%20by%20the%20city%20government.%20The%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20called%20for%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20these%20alleged%20frauds%2C%20involving%20fake%20lab%20tests%20and%20%E2%80%98ghost%20patients'%20at%20Delhi%20Mohalla%20Clinics.%20A%20CBI%20investigation%20was%20also%20recommended%20into%20substandard%20drug%20samples%20collected%20from%20three%20government%20hospitals.%20These%20irregularities%20were%20identified%20through%20investigations%20conducted%20in%202023.%20It%20was%20found%20that%20patients%20at%20these%20Mohalla%20clinics%20were%20given%20consultations%20and%20medicines%20by%20unauthorised%20staff%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20fake%20mobile%20numbers%20were%20used%20to%20register%20patients%20and%20conduct%20lab%20tests.%20The%20health%20department's%20inquiry%20report%20showed%20that%20over%203%2C000%20records%20of%20different%20patients%20had%20the%20same%20mobile%20number%E2%80%949999999999%E2%80%94while%20for%20999%20patients%2C%20their%20mobile%20numbers%20were%20repeated%2015%20or%20more%20times.%20Similarly%2C%2011%2C657%20patients%20had%20the%20mobile%20number%20%E2%80%9Czero%E2%80%9D%20registered%20against%20their%20names%2C%20while%20over%208%2C000%20patients%20had%20blank%20mobile%20number%20fields%20in%20their%20registration%20records.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20AAP's%20claims%20about%20improving%20education%20are%20also%20under%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20two%20departments%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20published%20public%20advertisements%20debunking%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20and%20her%20political%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20about%20the%20Sanjeevni%20and%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojna.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20government%20departments%20have%20publicly%20challenged%20their%20own%20chief%20minister's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20is%20also%20facing%20a%20challenge%20to%20several%20unfulfilled%20promises%2C%20such%20as%20cleaning%20the%20Yamuna%2C%20riverfront%20development%2C%20the%20Gazipur%20dump%20yard%2C%20pollution%20control%2C%20and%20providing%20tap%20water%20to%20all.%20Inflated%20electricity%20and%20water%20bills%20have%20raised%20concerns%20among%20certain%20sections%20of%20Delhi's%20residents.%20Though%20Kejriwal%20has%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20pay%20the%20bills%20and%20promised%20to%20waive%20them%20off%20if%20he%20returns%20to%20power%2C%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20why%20were%20inflated%20bills%20issued%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20and%20if%20they%20were%20issued%2C%20why%20weren't%20they%20corrected%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20the%20poll%20schedule%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi's%20public%20statement%2C%20that%20she%20is%20holding%20the%20post%20temporarily%20until%20the%20elections%2C%20may%20not%20add%20value%20to%20the%20AAP's%20campaign.%20There%20is%20a%20lingering%20question%20about%20whether%20Kejriwal%2C%20if%20the%20AAP%20manages%20to%20win%20again%2C%20can%20assume%20office%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20bail%20conditions%20imposed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Kejriwal%20clearly%20stated%20that%20he%20could%20not%20enter%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20sign%20official%20files%20in%20that%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20