%20about%20the%20risks%2C%20and%20they%20faced%20rejection%20at%20an%20entrepreneurship%20boot%20camp%20for%20lacking%20financial%20know-how.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%2C%20but%20it%20made%20us%20look%20at%20our%20product%20differently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20hurdles%2C%20they%20pushed%20forward.%20They%20refined%20their%20design%20after%20early%20users%20mistook%20the%20natural%20brown%20colour%20of%20the%20fibre%20for%20dirt.%20By%202018%2C%20they%20launched%20%3Cem%3EBliss%20Naturals%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Starting%20as%20a%20two-person%20team%20handling%20everything%20themselves%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20now%20grown%20into%20a%2050-member%20operation%20in%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20rash-free%20periods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20redesigning%20the%20product%20to%20have%20a%20cleaner%2C%20whiter%20top%20layer%2C%20the%20brand%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20convincing%20customers%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio-based%20alternative%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20everything%20changed%20during%20the%20Coimbatore%20Codissia%20shopping%20festival%20in%20December%202018%2C%20where%20they%20gained%201%2C000%20customers%20in%20just%2010%20days!%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20our%20biggest%20breakthrough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Niveda%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpana%20Sarathi%20from%20Tiruppur%2C%20a%20loyal%20Bliss%20customer%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20always