ades%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20through%20waves%20of%20conflict%20posed%20by%20communities%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20game%20and%20stepping%20closer%20to%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Bring%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20the%20conservation%20of%20tigers%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20easy%20until%20he%20had%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops.%20And%20the%20story%20of%20how%20he%20compelled%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20consider%20protecting%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20puts%20this%20never-die-spirit%20into%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrinda%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20duo%20would%20often%20correspond%20with%20each%20other%20through%20postcards.%20She%20then%20proceeds%20to%20read%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Duff%20Hart-Davis%E2%80%99%20biography%2C%20which%20confirms%20the%20story%20of%20Billy%20Arjan%20standing%20up%20to%20bureaucracy%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20safeguard%20the%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%20100vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%20petitioned%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20bring%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917.jpg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0003_IMG0022-350x350-1-1735221917-200x200.jpg%20200w