ard%20seeds%2C%20which%20boosted%20my%20income%2C%20and%20trained%20me%20to%20operate%20machines%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20steady%20job.%20Now%2C%20my%20children%20are%20receiving%20an%20education%2C%20and%20one%20is%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20Veterinary%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20treated%20as%20partners%2C%20not%20just%20suppliers.%20They%20have%20a%20direct%20stake%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20ensures%20that%20they%20are%20as%20invested%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20business%20as%20we%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%2C%20building%20a%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20significant%20challenges%20as%20they%20expanded%20their%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20raise%20funds%20after%20becoming%20a%20private%20limited%20company.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20impact%20investors%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20entrepreneurship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20their%20inexperience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driven%20by%20willpower%2C%20but%20we%20had%20little%20experience%20and%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20skills.%20We%20realised%20that%20skills%20are%20developed%20through%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20mentoring%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20major%20challenge%20came%20when%20the%20trio%20encountered%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20taken%20a%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20loan%20to%20procure%20oil%20from%20farme