0a%20two-day-old%20female%20child%20near%20the%20Governmental%20Hospital.%20The%20parents%20had%20left%20a%20note%20saying%20this%20child%20is%20HIV%20positive%20and%20is%20a%20disgrace%20to%20the%20family.%20I%20decided%20to%20provide%20a%20good%20living%20for%20the%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20recalling%20the%20incident%20that%20happened%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20was%20to%20help%20children%20with%20HIV%20understand%20that%20it%20was%20just%20another%20health%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20disease%20to%20define%20them.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20the%20same%20care%20and%20respect%20as%20any%20other%20child.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20are%20brought%20in%20by%20their%20parents%2C%20some%20are%20abandoned%2C%20and%20some%20are%20sent%20from%20hospitals%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20been%20able%20to%20save%20over%20400%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277718%2Fnakshatra-changemaker-inspiring-transwoman-bengaluru-destitute-orphans-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20affected%20by%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20helped%20them%20with%20education%2C%20medicines%2C%20food%2C%20shelter%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20love%20and%20affection.%20Noori%20has%20invested%20in%20a%20space%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20All%20I%20do%20right%20now%20is%20for%20them%20and%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoori%20%3Cem%3Eaaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grandma)%20has%20always%20prioritised%20education%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20study%20three%20degrees%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naga%20Thejas%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20at%20SIP%20Memorial%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%2C%20hoping%20to%20start%20his%20own%20NGO%20to%20support%20people%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Activities%20conducted%20for%20the%20children%20at%20the%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20comfortable%20at%20SIP%20home%20as%20I%20used%20to%20get%20healthy%20and%20delicious%20meals%20every%20day.%20I%20also%20had%20my%20friends%2C%20with%20whom%20time%20would%20fly%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naga%2C%20sharing%20the%20joy%20of%20growing%20in%20the%20safe%20space%20created%20by%20Noori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20proud%20to%20say%20that%20I%20am%20the%20first%20transgender%20to%20own%20a%20passport%20and%20a%20ration%20card%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori%2C%20who%20currently%20holds%2022%20leadership%20positions%20for%20multiple%20organisations%20and%2