20the%20remote%20reaches%20of%20Chirang%20district%2C%20Assam.%20Today%2C%20at%2062%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20survivor%2C%20but%20a%20trailblazer%2C%20earning%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20revolutionary%20work%20in%20agriculture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20eight%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20five%20brothers%20and%20three%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20life%20in%20Panbari%2C%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Chirang%20district%2C%20was%20difficult%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20His%20parents%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20labourers%20on%20construction%20sites%20and%20at%20landowners%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20did%20their%20best%20to%20care%20for%20their%20children%2C%20but%20resources%20were%20scarce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20we%20got%20lucky%2C%20they%20would%20find%20some%20work%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20goodwill%20of%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20was%20a%20small%20settlement%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20forest.%20Because%20of%20the%20forest%20animals%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20cultivate%20any%20food%20for%20ourselves%3B%20as%20they%20would%20destroy%20the%20crops.%20We%20only%20had%20two%20choices%3A%20either%20become%20a%20labourer%20or%20head%20into%20the%20jungle%20to%20collect%20wild%20potatoes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20was%20no%20concept%20of%20a%20market%2C%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20to%20ask%20the%20landowners%20or%20wealthier%20people%20for%20rice%3B%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99d%20eat.%20I%20grew%20up%20eating%20that%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E